aiHub.name: aiHub
aiHub.contactinfo: Engineering MIB Administrator Postal: Applied Innovation Inc. 5800 Innovation Drive Dublin, OH 43016-3271 Tel: 614/798-2000 Fax: 614/798-1770 E-mail: snmp@aiinet.com
aiHub.description: The MIB Module for Ethernet hubs

aiHubTwistedPairPortNumber.name: aiHubTwistedPairPortNumber
aiHubTwistedPairPortNumber.description: The number of twisted-pair hub ports. By convention, these are the lower numbered hub ports.

aiHubNonTwistedPairPortNumber.name: aiHubNonTwistedPairPortNumber
aiHubNonTwistedPairPortNumber.description: The number of non-twisted-pair hub ports.

aiHubPortTable.name: aiHubPortTable
aiHubPortTable.description: A list of hub Ethernet port entries.

aiHubPortEntry.name: aiHubPortEntry
aiHubPortEntry.description: Hub parameter values for an Ethernet port.

aiHubPortIndex.name: aiHubPortIndex
aiHubPortIndex.description: An index value that uniquely identifies a port. The port identified by a particular value of this index is the same port as identified by portBasicID in hmBasicPortTable in the IEEE Hub MIB. Corresponds directly to the numbered, twisted-pair port numbers and indirectly to the unnumbered, non-twisted-pair ports (A, C) in the diagnostic display.

aiHubPortName.name: aiHubPortName
aiHubPortName.description: An administratively assigned name for a twisted-pair port, typically with some local significance. Corresponds directly to the WINSLC PORTNAME string.

aiHubPortAdminState.name: aiHubPortAdminState
aiHubPortAdminState.description: Control over the port's ability to transmit and receive. ENABLED/DISABLED.

aiHubPortAutoPartitionState.name: aiHubPortAutoPartitionState
aiHubPortAutoPartitionState.description: The port's status with regard to automatic partitioning.

aiHubPortErrors.name: aiHubPortErrors
aiHubPortErrors.description: The number of times that a frame was received in erorr.

aiHubPortCollisions.name: aiHubPortCollisions
aiHubPortCollisions.description: Number of times that a frame collision came within the allowed collision window.

aiHubPortLinkErrors.name: aiHubPortLinkErrors
aiHubPortLinkErrors.description: Number of times that a link error was detected.

aiHubPortShortPackets.name: aiHubPortShortPackets
aiHubPortShortPackets.description: Number of times that a short packet was detected.

aiHubPortJabbers.name: aiHubPortJabbers
aiHubPortJabbers.description: Number of times that a jabber packet ??? was detected.

aiHubPortPartition.name: aiHubPortPartition
aiHubPortPartition.description: Number of times that this port was AutoPartitioned.

aiHubPortZero.name: aiHubPortZero
aiHubPortZero.description: Control to zero Counters kept for the port. In response to a get-request or get-next-request, the agent always returns 'ready' for this value. Setting the value to 'ready' has no effect. Setting it to 'execute' causes all the system's Counters to be zeroed. Corresponds to the ZERO PORT command.

aiHubPortZeroTime.name: aiHubPortZeroTime
aiHubPortZeroTime.description: The time the counters for this port was last zeroed.

aiHubLogMessage.name: aiHubLogMessage
aiHubLogMessage.description: Any string 'set' into this variable will force a log message to be printed on the CLC log.

aiHubPortAutoPartitionLimit.name: aiHubPortAutoPartitionLimit
aiHubPortAutoPartitionLimit.description: The hub AutoPartition limit, 31 or 63 collisions.
